### Short Dramatic Reveals
‚ùå **Avoid**: "The answer? Three simple steps."
‚ùå **Avoid**: "The key? Consistency."
‚ùå **Avoid**: "My approach? Start small."
‚úÖ **Good**: "I found three steps that actually worked."
